message: On Friday, Aug 25, we were privileged to attend the 2017 Hispanic Women of Distinction Awards. Rachel Tourgeman was one of the 12 amazing women that were honorees. The event was incredible down to the very detail. Elaine Vazquez and her team put on an outstanding production. Congratulations to all the women honored and thank you for all that you do for our community!
